name: Anime Extract
description:
Anime extract will tune your generations towards flat shaded anime-like look. Previews generated with SaluteMix.

This is an extracted lora of a merge done by a discord user DarkSide from detailedproject and animelike 2.5D. Similar effort can be found here. In comparison the A1Filter, this extract tunes to a flat style more effectively.

This extract was done against aom2_nsfw and the soft version was done against novel's model.

Huggingface: https://huggingface.co/SirVeggie/anime_extract
